issue.title: Add real-world Less libs to tests
issue.body:
While Less has hundreds of tests, sometimes real-world Less libraries do things that are unexpected, which breaks them with new releases - https://github.com/ant-design/ant-design/issues/7850#issuecomment-399904195

It wouldn't be too much work to pull a few popular Less libs (via NPM) and add them to the testing suite, especially since `@import` can pull from NPM by default (in Node) in 3.0+.
